# Self-contained node bundle: Claude Desktop runs `node ${__dirname}/dist/mcp/index.js`
# (see manifest.json mcp_config) with its OWN bundled Node — no npx, no network, no
# system Node, works on Windows/macOS/Linux. So the bundle MUST ship dist + a flat
# production node_modules (staged by scripts/bundle.mjs). We only strip the source,
# tests, and dev toolchain. node_modules is INTENTIONALLY shipped — do not re-add it.
src
test
bench
desktop
docs
.github
.git
.claude
*.local.md
*.test.*
tsconfig.json
eslint.config.*
.gitignore
.mcpbignore
pnpm-lock.yaml
*.mcpb
